enience\n\t\t\t\t\t- Render backfaces\n\t\t\t\t\t- Hide Grid\n\t\t\t\t- Mesh Toolkit:\n\t\t\t\t\t- Split by Materials\n\t\t\t\t\t- Split by Adjacency\n\t\t\t\t- UV\n\t\t\t\t\t- UV unwrap: 2048\n\t\t\t\t\t- UV pack: 2048\n\t\t\t\t- Optimize: highest\n\t\t\t\t- Remesh\n\t\t\t\t\t- Mode: optimize\n\t\t\t\t\t- Fuzzy Face Count Target: high\n\t\t\t- Blender\n\t\t\t\t- when imported: the whole model shares one material (we will split that into components)\n\t\t\t\t- model looks horrible: change to material view\n\t\t\t\t- model still looks horrible: change normal map from \"tangent space\" to \"model space\"\n\t\t\t\t- Color und Alpha löschen (evtl gar nicht erst mit baken)\n\t\t\t\t- Materialien duplizieren\n\t\t\t\t\t- change values\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- Evtl Addon von Stefan Seelinger, dass die CSV Parameter speichert wie Roughness etc?\n\t\t\t\t- pack\n\t\t\t- Omniverse\n\t\t\t\t- Mesh ersetzen in .usd file?\n\t\t- ### Workflow: Provide Assets fast that look better than ever but are not optimized\n\t\t\t- InstaLOD\n\t\t\t\t- Import: Z up\n\t\t\t\t- Mesh Toolkit: Split by Adjaceny\n\t\t\t\t\t- Delete weird cylinders\n\t\t\t\t- UV unwrap\n\t\t\t\t- UV pack\n\t\t\t\t- export .fbx\n\t\t\t- Blender\n\t\t\t\t- Materialien\n\t\t\t\t\t- reduzieren\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- umbennen\n\t\t\t\t\t- verbessern\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- komische Shader ersetzen\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- normal maps löschen\n\t\t\t\t\t- purge\n\t\t\t\t\t- Materialien als Assets speichern\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- /asset library/worl/material library blender\n\t\t\t\t- .blend speichern\n\t\t\t\t\t- Asset Library/work/<robotername>\n\t\t\t- Omniverse\n\t\t\t\t- Rig\n\t\t\t\t- Material\n\t\t\t\t\t- Rougness Maps\n\t\t\t\t\t- Normal Map",536872690]],["^15",[239,"^1@",1721025768583,536870916]],["^15",[239,"^1A","~m1721134287001",536872689]],["^15",[239,"^Z","journals/2024_06_19.md",536870916]],["^15",[240,"^K",1721025768582,536870916]],["^15",[240,"^[",239,536870916]],["^15",[240,"^N",20240619,536870916]],["^15",[240,"^@",true,536870916]],["^15",[240,"^Y