Robot Pilot]]\n  :LOGBOOK:\n  CLOCK: [2024-05-31 Fri 09:36:20]--[2024-05-31 Fri 09:36:21] =>  00:00:01\n  CLOCK: [2024-05-31 Fri 11:42:59]--[2024-05-31 Fri 11:43:15] =>  00:00:16\n  CLOCK: [2024-05-31 Fri 11:43:23]--[2024-05-31 Fri 11:43:24] =>  00:00:01\n  :END:\n- ### [[Protokoll]]\n  people:: [[Paul Weiss]] [[Stefan Wagner]] [[Markus Schmidtchen]] [[Bruno Bellmann]] \n  projekt:: [[Asset Library]]\n\t- Mit Stefan Wagner zusammen setzen für Blender\n\t\t- Mein Workflow - viele Addons\n\t\t\t- USD OV Connector\n\t\t\t- Machin3tools zeigen: Rigging\n\t\t\t- Hypercursor wäre perfekt für das Erstellen von Collidern\n\t\t\t- Hard Ops für Origins etc.\n\t\t\t- Meine Studio HDRIs verwenden: in allen Anwendungen der gleiche Look\n\t\t- Plan - schau mer mal\n\t\t\t- InstaMAT - sehr viel günstiger als Substance\n\t\t\t- InstaLOD\n\t- Goldener Standard - UR5\n\t- Collision Objects - in Blender oder von OV generieren lassen?\n\t\t- Paul Weiss in OV\n\t\t- Stefan Wagner und ich in Blender\n\t- Test Modell\n\t\t- ABB IRB1300 [Beispiel](https://www.pandct.com/uploads/news_images/ABB%2026721.jpg)\n\t- DH-Parameter\n\t\t- Werden von Robotics geschickt\n\t\t\t- Immer um Z drehen\n\t\t\t  id:: 66588008-2900-49b2-9dbc-0f76cfd07f6b\n\t\t\t- Base kann ganz wo anders sein\n\t\t\t- Sieht man alles im Rigging Video Tutorial (Slack)\n\t\t- GLB Texture Tools - Addon für **Ambient Occlusion**\n\t\t- gltf export\n\t\t\t- compression\n\t\t\t- [Gltf Confverter](https://.gltf.pmnd.rs) - Link brauche ich\n\t\t\t- threejs\n\t\t\t- codesandbox\n\t\t\t- react drei library\n\t- [[TODO/Asset Library]]\n\t  :LOGBOOK:\n\t  CLOCK: [2024-05-31 Fri 09:36:34]\n\t  :END:\n\t-\n- ### [[Protokoll]]\n  people:: [[Michael Graf]] [[Johannes Baumgärtel]]\n  projekt:: [[MPI]]\n\t- CAD Modell wird angefragt\n\t\t- Spinning Disk nicht von Zeiss\n\t\t- Hamamatsu (?) Kamera nicht von Zeiss\n\t- Feedack an MPI - Zeiss kann seinen Teil beitragen\n\t- Zeiss fragt, ob wir an Kooperationen interssiert sind - what - the - fuck - weil ich ein 3D-Modell angefragt habe. Ich glaubs kaum\n\t\t- Michael Graf fragt unter welchen Bedingungen er das raus geben kann\n\t\t\t- Upscaling\n\t\t\t- Durchsatz\n\t\t\t- Automatisierung\n\t\t- \"Unsere Entwickler sterben auch nicht an langeweile\" - schau mer mal obs klappt mit den Ressoucen\n\t-\n- ### [[Design Sprint]]\n\t- Mit Nina, in Obsidian",536870916]],["^15",[757,"^1@",1721025768759,536870916]],["^15",[757,"^Z","journals/2024_05_30.md",536870916]],["^15",[758,"^K",1721025768758,536870916]],["^15",[758,"^[",757,536870916]],["^15",[758,"^N",20240530,536870916]],["^15",[758,"^@",true,536870916]],["^15",[758,"^Y","2024-05-30",536870916]],["^15",[758,"^11","2024-05-30",536870916]],["^15",[758,"^B",1721025768758,536870916]],["^15",[758,"^;","~u6694c4e8-ce6e-4cfb-aff4-3f02a2c5ba99",536870916]],["^15",[759,"^K",1721025768758,536870916]],["^15",[759,"^@",false,536870916]],["^15",[759,"^Y","michael graf",536870916]],["^15",[759,"^11","Michael Graf",536870916]],["^15",[759,"^B",1721025768758,536870916]],["^15",[759,"^;","~u6694c4e8-a60c-40e0-a329-49d40e30129b",536870916]],["^15",[760,"^K",1721025768757,536870916]],["^15",[760,"^@",false,536870916]],["^15",[760,"^Y","markus schmidtchen",536870916]],["^15",[760,"^11","Markus Schmidtchen",536870916]],["^15",[760,"^B",1721025768757,536870916]],["^15",[760,"^;","~u6694c4e8-65ef-41b7-b948-8fe03855c46c",536870916]],["^15",[761,"^K",1721025768816,536870916]],["^15",[761,"^[",866,536870916]],["^15",[761,"^@",false,536870916]],["^15",[761,"^Y","design sprint",536870916]],["^15",[761,"^11","Design Sprint",536870916]],["^15",[761,"^B",1721025768816,536870916]],["^15",[761,"^;","~u6694c4e8-12dd-4ef0-8707-a4406ab0b39e",536870916]],["^15",[762,"^Q","threejs",536870916]],["^15",[762,"^O","^16",536870916]],["^15",[762,"^F",792,536870916]],["^15",[762,"^X",758,536870916]],["^15",[762,"^V",797,536870916]],["^15",[762,"^U",42,536870916]],["^15",[762,"^U",43,536870916]],["^15",[762,"^U",45,536870916]],["^15",[762,"^U",47,53687